flowchart LR
    A["1. Analytical and<br/>Monte Carlo Evaluation<br/>ARL • false alarms • detection delay"]
    B["2. Retrospective Replay<br/>Historical data • expert adjudication<br/>contextual classification"]
    C["3. Shadow-Mode Deployment<br/>No operational intervention<br/>evidence packages and recommendations"]
    D["4. Bounded Pilot<br/>Low-risk workflows only<br/>policy and human-factor evaluation"]
    E["5. Scaled Evaluation<br/>Multi-site comparison<br/>operational outcomes"]
    F["Revise or Stop<br/>Unsafe false dismissals<br/>policy failures • poor usability"]

    A --> B --> C --> D --> E
    B -. failure threshold .-> F
    C -. failure threshold .-> F
    D -. failure threshold .-> F
    F -. redesign and revalidation .-> A
